collection.name: Cyber Gorillas Official
collection.description:
The CyberGorillas is a collection of 3333 randomly generated Cyber-themed Gorillas, featuring 333 Genesis CyberGorillas amongst them. 

Key focus on function-backed utility, partnerships and tools. Priority on burning & deflationary mechanics.

Gamified marketplace & auction house coming soon.

[CyberKings ](https://opensea.io/collection/cyberkingsofficial) │  [Baby CyberGorillas](https://opensea.io/collection/baby-cybergorillas-v2) │ [CyberBananas](https://opensea.io/collection/cyberbananas)


Your NFTs may accumulate a utility token (“CYBER”) when they are staked in the smart contract. CYBER has no other functionality other than within the Cyber Gorillas ecosystem, and it cannot be purchased from Cyber Gorillas Developers. The Cyber Gorillas Developers do not provide or intend to provide a secondary marketplace for CYBER..
